<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>By Mail on Sunday Reporter   Updated:  02:11, 22 May 2011</p>

<p>On May 15 we said Tim Henman was being paid £200,000 by the BBC for commentating at Wimbledon this year.</p>

